ty is covered with sandal paste(Chandanam) throughout the year except on Vaishaka Sudda Thadiya. On this auspicious day, the main deity givesNijapada Darshan( the true form of God ) for 12hrs only.\\u2028Legend has it that the Ugra form of Narasimha as he killed the demon\\u00a0<strong>Hiranyakashipu<\\/strong>\\u00a0was so fierce that the image is kept covered by sandal paste throughout the year. History says that Prahlada \\u2013 a devotee of Lord Vishnu was being tortoured by his father. Lord Vishnu in the avatara of Lord Nrusimha kills Prahlada\\u2019s father and saves the child.<\\/p>\",\"typography_typography\":\"custom\",\"typography_font_family\":\"Montserrat\",\"typography_font_weight\":\"400\",\"text_color\":\"#000000\",\"_margin\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"top\":\"46\",\"right\":\"0\",\"bottom\":\"0\",\"left\":\"-74\",\"isLinked\":false}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"4dd1b2c\",\"elType\":\"container\",\"settings\":{\"flex_direction\":\"row\",\"background_overlay_background\":\"classic\",\"min_height\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"size\":555,\"sizes\":[]},\"background_background\":\"classic\",\"background_color\":\"#FFF9CF\",\"background_overlay_image\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/simhachalam\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2025\\/09\\/Vector-6.png\",\"id\":142,\"size\":\"\",\"alt\":\"\",\"source\":\"library\"},\"background_overlay_position\":\"initial\",\"background_overlay_xpos\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"size\":85,\"sizes\":[]},\"background_overlay_ypos\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"size\":15,\"sizes\":[]},\"background_overlay_repeat\":\"no-repeat\",\"background_overlay_size\":\"initial\",\"background_overlay_bg_width\":{\"unit\":\"%\",\"size\":35,\"sizes\":[]},\"background_overlay_opacity\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"size\":0.85,\"sizes\":[]}},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"7e9d335\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"_element_width\":\"initial\",\"_element_custom_width\":{\"unit\":\"%\",\"size\":44.517},\"_flex_size\":\"none\",\"image\":{\"url\":\"