(29, 1, '2025-09-02 08:19:23', '2025-09-02 08:19:23', '<img width=\"569\" height=\"114\" src=\"http://localhost/simhachalam/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/aptdc-new-logo-cl-1.png\" alt=\"\" />													<p>With APTDC, you can book a complete travel package that offers a divine visit to the sacred <strong>Simhachalam Temple</strong> along with a scenic and cultural tour of Visakhapatnam. This thoughtfully curated package includes visits to spiritual landmarks like <strong>Malyadri Lakshmi Narasimha Swamy Temple</strong> and <strong>Sri Venkateswara Alayam</strong>, as well as popular attractions like <strong>Tenneti Park</strong>, the <strong>Visakha Museum</strong>, and many more.</p><p>Enjoy comfortable, affordable accommodations with exclusive offersall bundled into one seamless experience. Whether you\'re seeking spiritual peace or scenic beauty, this journey has it all.</p><p>
